 dataвҶҗGenerateTestData n;NotFixedKeys;event;event_type;keywords;lipsum;organisation;person;person_names;presentation;presentation_media;presentation_type;presenter;stems;thing_names;videos;youtube_video
вҚқ Insert dummy data into the database for testing
вҚқ First tests considered:
вҚқ - /videos?search= should return all videos with matching terms
вҚқ - /videos?presenter=p_name should return all videos by presenter p_name
вҚқ - /videos?search=p_name       should include videos by presenter p_name
вҚқ FIXME this is not comprehensive. Fields essential to the video library are used, but many are not.

вҚқ Start by generating joined data and deconstructing it into the normalised database, then loop over each table and insert.

вҚқ CONFIG
 keywordsвҶҗgenerator.keywords
 stemsвҶҗgenerator.stemmable[;2]
 person_namesвҶҗ'Geoff' 'Streeter' 'John' 'Scholes' 'Iverson' 'Dolor' 'Fugiat' 'Orange' 'Rich' 'Park' 'Jada' 'Andrade' 'Andy' 'Karen' 'Fiona' 'Jason' 'Peter' 'Silas'
 thing_namesвҶҗ'APL' 'Meeting' 'Seeds' 'Conference' 'Dyalog' 'Alpha' 'Omega'
 lipsumвҶҗgenerator.lipsum

вҚқ GENERATE
 вҺ•RLвҶҗ42

вҚқ Use вҺ•DF to give each namespace a name that can be used to look up into SQL table metadata
 event_typeвҶҗ(
     type:(vocab:keywords вӢ„ max:1)generator.Name n
     description:(vocab:lipsum вӢ„ max:65535)generator.Text n
     url_slug:generator.URL n
 )
 event_type.вҺ•DF'event_type'

 eventвҶҗ()
 event.titleвҶҗ(vocab:thing_names вӢ„ max:2)generator.NameвҚЈ{вҲ§/вү вҚө}n
 event.(start end)вҶҗgenerator.DateTimeВЁ2вҚҙn
 event.typeвҶҗ?nвҚҙn
 event.url_slugвҶҗ'-'@(' 'вҲҳ=)ВЁВҜ1 вҺ•C event.title
 event.вҺ•DF'event'
 example_eventвҶҗвҠғevent.url_slug   вҚқ Use example_event in DummyData.TestGETVideos_EventShortname

 organisationвҶҗ()
 organisation.nameвҶҗ(vocab:thing_names вӢ„ max:1)generator.Name n
 organisation.вҺ•DF'organisation'

 personвҶҗ()
 person.nameвҶҗ(vocab:person_names вӢ„ max:3)generator.Name n
 person.organisation_idвҶҗ?nвҚҙn
 person.вҺ•DF'person'

 presentation_typeвҶҗ(type:(вҠӮ?nвҚҙвүўkeywords)вҢ·keywords)
 presentation_type.вҺ•DF'presentation_type'

 presentationвҶҗ()
 presentation.event_idвҶҗ?nвҚҙn-1   вҚқ events 1..n-1 only; event n guaranteed no presentations вҶ’ has_videos=0
 presentation.event_id[вҚі6]вҶҗ1    вҚқ presentation 1 вҶ’ event 1; combined with fixed_keys, event 1 has has_videos=1
 presentation.codeвҶҗ(vocab:вҺ•A,вҺ•D вӢ„ max:2 вӢ„ unique:1)generator.Name n
 presentation.titleвҶҗstems
 presentation.title,вҶҗ(vocab:lipsum вӢ„ max:30)generator.Text n-вүўstems
 presentation.title[1],вҶҗвҠӮ' dolor'   вҚқ Ensure a keyword is present in search results
 presentation.type_idвҶҗ?nвҚҙn
 presentation.descriptionвҶҗ(vocab:lipsum вӢ„ max:65535)generator.Text n
 presentation.presented_atвҶҗ'2005-04-03 00:00:00' '2008-05-05 00:00:00' '2012-12-12 00:00:00',generator.DateTime n-3   вҚқ Fixed dates for testing date range filtering
 presentation.вҺ•DF'presentation'

 presenterвҶҗ()
 вҚқ Using fixed keys in the presenter and presentation_media tables ensures that stems are found in video results for testing
 presenter.(presentation_id person_id)вҶҗfixed_keysвҶҗ(1 2 3 3)(1 2 3 4)   вҚқ presentation 1 has presenter 1; presentation 2 has presenter 2; presentation 3 has presenters 3 and 4
 NotFixedKeysвҶҗ{~вҲЁ/,(вҚүвҶ‘fixed_keys)вҚ·вҚӨ1 2вҠўвҚө}
 presenter.(presentation_id person_id),вҶҗвҶ“вҚү{?вҚөвҚҙвҚӣвҚҙn}вҚЈ{(NotFixedKeys вҚә)вҲ§вҲ§/вү вҚә}(n-вүўfixed_keys)2вҚҙ0
 presenter.вҺ•DF'presenter'

 вҚқ Videos is not a table to insert, but its data is used in other tables and must be consistent, so we create it here and re-use it below
 videosвҶҗ()
 example_search_termвҶҗ'wombo'
 videos.titleвҶҗexample_search_termвҠӮвҚӣ,stems   вҚқ Unique keyword for search testing
 videos.title,вҶҗ(vocab:lipsum вӢ„ max:30)generator.Text n-1+вүўstems
 videos.descriptionвҶҗ(vocab: lipsum вӢ„ max: 65535)generator.Text n
 videos.description[2]вҶҗvideos.description[1]   вҚқ Guarantee similar video for recommendations test
 videos.youtube_idвҶҗвҶ“{(вҺ•A,вҺ•C вҺ•A)[?вҚөвҚҙвҚӣвҚҙ2Г—26]}вҚЈ{вҲ§/вү вҚә}n 11вҚҙ0
 example_videoвҶҗвҠғvideos.youtube_id   вҚқ Use example_video in DummyData.TestGETVideo

 presentation_mediaвҶҗ(type:nвҚҙвҠӮ'youtube_video')
 presentation_media.(presentation_id media_id)вҶҗfixed_keysвҶҗ(вҚі6)(вҚі6)
 presentation_media.(presentation_id media_id),вҶҗвҶ“вҚү{?вҚөвҚҙвҚӣвҚҙn n}вҚЈ{(NotFixedKeys вҚә)вҲ§(вҲ§/1<вҠў/вҚә)вҲ§вҲ§/вү вҚә}(n-вүўfixed_keys)2вҚҙ0   вҚқ Random unique pairs of numbers
 presentation_media.вҺ•DF'presentation_media'

 youtube_videoвҶҗ(
     youtube_id:videos.youtube_id
     title:videos.title
     description:videos.description
 )
 youtube_video.вҺ•DF'youtube_video'

вҚқ All generator functions take a right arg of number of records to generate
вҚқ Left argument is max size of data (length in bits), OR a special left argument for specific columns

 dataвҶҗevent_type event organisation person presentation_type presentation presenter presentation_media youtube_video
